.TH man 1  "12 Avril 2021" "0.0" "simple_shell man page"
.SH NAME
Simple_shell - a simple shell version that excutes a varity of commands
.SH SYNOPSIS
shell  [commands]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Simple_shell is an sh-compatible command language interpreter that executes commands read from the standard input 
or from a file. Simple_shell also incorporates useful features from the Korn and C shells (ksh and csh).
.SH OPTIONS
    cd  ,  cd "path NAME"
        change the current working directory

    ls , /bin/ls
        lists allq the files in working directory

    ls -l
        lists all the files in long list format

    CTRL-c 
        exiting the shell
.SH SEE ALSO
Nothing 
.SH BUGS
No known bugs.
